        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value>https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v49KB-6PDo-d4JPilD6UfehTPccouzcKon2198TPy3vDft3hG0jvrP4K564lKv-PHsQCzst-aTR3jj5n9gwsGlN_nzjuNecZRCmFJK-o7PX5Jxr77fj-B2cnrnexdmUXNUhT9NERp1DvXIww07kv-KpWQ</value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            -122.867875,45.556747,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Big Creek Reservoir #1</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v7YhQ8aioAlwoYuP3F8UkQSdLa18yPPMErqXIGOwrZctvECJpM8aJPm20iUr62hEgbbuvzEYKlEGsOJOqymoCyXrNM4ccgz_jORNezYnOxHeB978RXltKYpVX09CV31PuGd3KTEw2pF9EkHaemzJkoEWS8v7z60kxc" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>This is a 20-acre reservoir on Big Creek Road northeast of Newport, offering year-round fishing. <br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout, bass, brown bullhead<br>Trout Stocking Schedule - https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=BIG+CR+RES-1&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31]]></description>
