      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Big Creek Reservoir #2</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v5kfZNP9-0RrYv_o-5nlju57jOmzDVXsfsqFC2YfkU1pZfosypst_rWVZb6hP3JwA8SsML9C6At4xKJTO3i20pA9aNfd9EkQ66zncpdeH5mNGlKGEOoj-MaGMV4s9LZSfqtHzSWJrvaV8oQYSDHJQjSMueW9n3PV1HY" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>The larger of the two reservoirs on Big Creek Road northeast of Newport, offering year-round fishing. <br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout, bass, brown bullhead <br><br>Trout Stocking Schedule -https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=BIG+CR+RES-2&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31 ]]></description>
