      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Breitenbush River - Breitenbush Campground</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6U-5LI8A-cgObXVNcuAGEClqhHNfwCxWSeb7FcQPz51jKnYbtKZ9PuEaD69bWLPyBry1s65pZ12GNDusB8wVD4WAOvKT0N3jqtWVXJBW8tiSQYebYbDxq4aZnj3a53cE6O91fPIc_YvAyaob86Iv8HlWIU6B2WMd3ufhWAzIT-gb8" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Primitive U.S. Forest Service campground located next to the Breitenbush River, located about 10 miles northeast of Detroit.<br> <br>Amenities: picnic tables, toilets, drinking water fire grills, garbage service, 30 sites, 5 accessible sites.<br> <br>Fish species: rainbow trout<br> <br>Breitenbush Campground Map (http://www.fs.usda.gov/detailfull/willamette/recreation/camping-cabins/?cid=stelprdb5136312&width=full)<br> <br>Trout Stocking Schedule -https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=BREITENBUSH+R&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31 ]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-53</styleUrl>
