          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            -121.986351,44.782932,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Breitenbush River Bridge</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6mF2qiD6baSeRF86QKj7gshUWRQR0lpuCh4d78LrxNjbX4GjB_fijlQoN-diEIvxxbh6KLrjhoH5UUb-JK8COfpm-oVVzEHrbpE4bNqJt5iIEUPUQ_5Qv1smike53E1KHyj2Vg7vEgS9VBiw-HncGE5sfNLE_Aavg51JOL9g" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>A tributary to Detroit Reservoir. This site is at a bridge over the Breitenbush River. Fish are released directly from the bridge. There is a small amount of gravel parking next to the bridge but it is very limited.<br> <br>Fish species: rainbow trout<br> <br>Trout Stocking Schedule - https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=BREITENBUSH+R&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-53</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value>https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6mF2qiD6baSeRF86QKj7gshUWRQR0lpuCh4d78LrxNjbX4GjB_fijlQoN-diEIvxxbh6KLrjhoH5UUb-JK8COfpm-oVVzEHrbpE4bNqJt5iIEUPUQ_5Qv1smike53E1KHyj2Vg7vEgS9VBiw-HncGE5sfNLE_Aavg51JOL9g</value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
        <Point>
