      <Placemark>
        <name>Cape Meares Lake</name>
        <description><![CDATA[A 65-acre lake located 7 miles west and north of Tillamook, Ore., along Bay Ocean Rd. <br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout, largemouth bass, brown bullhead, bluegill, surplus hatchery steelhead when available<br><br>Trout Stocking Schedule -https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=CAPE+MEARES+LK&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31 ]]></description>
