      <Placemark>
        <name>Carter Lake</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v5IPbPssNUlUlm_qOsdIYPAmBMNRaSmD9lOmXae0YlZN6NxbmyJPBvkFV3fnzVoi95RRpKIuNtkuajZKecJLKe7TTmciXWz-vjIuZO_CAM8o3DJWm2wO7Se8Q1qagyT4jDLNu7DRIcubNGVk9GRYGly" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>A long, narrow 28-acre lake that lies parallel to and west of Hwy.101. Good bank access, protection from the wind, campground with easy access to dune.<br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout <br><br> <br>Trout Stocking Schedule - https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=CLEAWOX+LK&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31]]></description>
