      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[Detroit Lake - Kane's Marina]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v7ZQEwbvQYeGrM2YVdwHVkKkJsbBhv0VYpbhiqk-qTMQm0jyZOAneGSCC1Vs7ugZVFtud8sV_ZAucGkHcZm7r4frfyaXIoXCqwVZKHPIyQb2lf683zClUvy19LneK1DWokxb2jZ8M8DvWrgMCQ1lrM4_5UDqGHGpw" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Kane’s Marina is located on Detroit Lake 50 miles east of Salem. Detroit Lake is a prime recreation area easily accessible from both eastern Oregon and the Willamette Valley. At 1,600 feet above sea level, Detroit Lake is fed by clear mountain water that warms to perfect temperature for swimming, skiing, wakeboarding, tubing and other in-the-water activities during the summer months. <br><br>Kane’s Marina (http://www.kanesmarina.com/) is a private facility that offers 400 slips for seasonal and overnight moorage, 200 ft. of guest tie-up, seasonal and overnight RV spaces, boat rentals, fuel, and convenience store where fishing licenses and tackle are sold. <br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout<br>Trout Stocking Schedule -https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=DETROIT+RES&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31 ]]></description>
