          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Dune Lake</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v5IEto2XFRKVIjYc3DvCajbsgDf_hXD3r44E-kKOTAVuSB3LmD4NjAUqCALQzsfkvJO8z4tjnlAgycrpAr6X193D_svrOZ5RIbOt-0t73K_7E7yVo0oqz1oczhlbyJxd0w8erVQWvYzq31Il-P-" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Dune Lake is a 2-acre lake located 6.5 miles north of Florence, Ore., on Hwy. 101. There is a trail around the lake that provides ease of access to fishermen. <br><br> Fish species: rainbow trout<br>Trout Stocking Schedule -https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=DUNE+LK&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31 ]]></description>
