      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Freeway Lake - East</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v4jY0HGfp1YlrpKC_IjE-KwWXDBHVLWPyYjRle4347opCmtoczyisQTZN42YePWKGqDisDYgq4K4aA4K8NO9La5ZYwJ8AJxJp31eDd7SjuwmhAOo0axOLa8cI6jbBoSKPcL2FSlp6nfNzMo98JBC1ARi5xalEM" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Three ponds located along I-5 about 3 miles south of Albany. One of the ponds is west of the freeway. The other two are east of the freeway. Bank fishing opportunities are good for the two lakes to the east of I-5. Amenities include restrooms and boat ramp for the launching of small boats. Additional, recreational opportunities include paved bike trails, hiking and wildlife viewing. <br><br>Sarah Helmick State Recreation Site (http://www.oregonstateparks.org/park_138.php) is nearby. <br> <br>Fish species: rainbow trout<br>Trout Stocking Schedule -https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=FREEWAY+LK%2C+EAST&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31 ]]></description>
