            -124.151173,43.787826,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Erhart Lake</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v4-RERqkbF47puNhALBDE3a_brVy7dSLfaaaX-gbngJX9M9RadTVRHBtSpQrQND2meETsYKyGNct1UOWnHPV8RKQQ6s_C93gpdY-Nlb42CjvTrDpKEK_vGH5nXgwSTjdojLvLLbUj997uez6YSa_2c" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>This 5-acre lake is located about 8 miles south of Florence, Ore. on Hwy 101, adjacent to the west side of the highway. The lake is not marked by signs but is clearly visible through the trees on the west side of the highway. Parking is available at several turnouts along the highway. The shoreline is forested but brushy. The elevation of the lake is near sea level.<br> <br>NOTE: Google Maps incorrectly labels this lake as Loon Lake. However, this is, in fact, Erhart Lake. <br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout <br><br>Campgrounds: Waxmyrtle (http://www.fs.usda.gov/wps/portal/fsinternet/!ut/p/c4/04_SB8K8xLLM9MSSzPy8xBz9CP0os3gDfxMDT8MwRydLA1cj72BTJw8jAwjQL8h2VAQAzHJMsQ!!/?ss=110612&ttype=recarea&recid=42563&actid=50&navtype=BROWSEBYSUBJECT&position=BROWSEBYSUBJECT&navid=110000000000000&pnavid=&cid=null&pname=Oregon+Dunes+National+Recreation+Area+-+Waxmyrtle+Campground), Lagoon (http://www.fs.usda.gov/wps/portal/fsinternet/!ut/p/c4/04_SB8K8xLLM9MSSzPy8xBz9CP0os3gDfxMDT8MwRydLA1cj72BTJw8jAwjQL8h2VAQAzHJMsQ!!/?ss=110612&ttype=recarea&recid=42557&actid=31&navtype=BROWSEBYSUBJECT&position=BROWSEBYSUBJECT&navid=110000000000000&pnavid=&cid=null&pname=Oregon+Dunes+National+Recreation+Area+-+Lagoon+Campground), Drftwood II Campground (http://www.fs.usda.gov/wps/portal/fsinternet/!ut/p/c4/04_SB8K8xLLM9MSSzPy8xBz9CP0os3gDfxMDT8MwRydLA1cj72BTJw8jAwjQL8h2VAQAzHJMsQ!!/?ss=110612&ttype=recarea&recid=42527&actid=31&navtype=BROWSEBYSUBJECT&position=BROWSEBYSUBJECT&navid=110000000000000&pnavid=&cid=null&pname=Oregon+Dunes+National+Recreation+Area+-+Driftwood+II+Campground), Oregon Dunes National Recreation Area (http://www.fs.usda.gov/wps/portal/fsinternet/!ut/p/c5/04_SB8K8xLLM9MSSzPy8xBz9CP0os3gDfxMDT8MwRydLA1cj72DTgBAjAwgAykeaxcN4jhYG_h4eYX5hPgYwefy6w0H24dcPNgEHcDTQ9_PIz03VL8iNMMgycVQEAObEnGA!/dl3/d3/L2dJQSEvUUt3QS9ZQnZ3LzZfME80MEkxVkFCOTBFMktTNUJIMjAwMDAwMDA!/?navtype=BROWSEBYSUBJECT&recid=42465&actid=&navid=110000000000000&pnavid=&ss=110612&position=&ttype=recarea&pname=Siuslaw%20National%20Forest%20-%20Oregon%20Dunes%20National%20Recreation%20Area). Honeyman State Park (http://www.oregonstateparks.org/park_134.php).<br> <br>ODFW Recreation Report & regulation updates (http://myodfw.com/recreation-report/fishing-report/northwest-zone)<br>Trout Stocking Schedule (http://www.dfw.state.or.us/resources/fishing/trout_stocking_schedules/)<br>Fishing Regulations (http://www.eregulations.com/oregon/fishing/)]]></description>
