      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Foster Reservoir - Calkins Boat Ramp</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v4UOO3t_ZqBqBWtbu1NgUsdU4MlYPI8-9yH_888hIzEln2w5x1T1zK0GU6ND39PLYKkbewHJeN-XBYcwr5sjRsLZQjoFLzKDqhfrev4j0yjlnORKw-yT5B40iB8GIP0N2wxlJG5o5zq4Cn4BP8jJBBUJjHrd27dDqaSiku_sQ" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>This boat ramp is approximately two miles out of Sweet Home on Hwy. 20 Large asphalt parking lot, restroom, and paved boat ramp. Calkins Boat Ramp (http://www.co.linn.or.us/parks/parks/caulkins.html) is maintained by the Linn County Parks Department.<br> <br>Fish species: rainbow trout, kokanee, bass <br> <br>Trout Stocking Schedule - https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=FOSTER+RES&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-53</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
