      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Foster Reservoir - Sunnyside County Park</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6iMBt1ZNx2LyWsyWRYqVJ2RLNW0C4BSi4I0Yg5X4MO1og_U96gqbQDlHUfLaKIkdIHn4BalDLCYl6leSpuZ5DJ5EG9aoOTAeOnL2dKSojP5X0uJImXwDhOf_bs7K0ZEqQZig3UVWGFp8zU8JLFKv_31rwJP98ZEldaqP2WiAiR" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>This is the largest park on Foster Reservoir east of Sweet Home. Amenities include a boat ramp, boat moorage, RV/tent/group campsites, off-leash dog park, stocked fishing ponds, dump station, showers, picnic shelters, playgrounds, sand vollebyall court <br> <br>Fish species: rainbow trout, kokanee, bass<br> <br>More information (http://www.co.linn.or.us/parks/parks/sunnyside.html)<br>Park map (http://www.co.linn.or.us/parks/parks/documents/SunnysideFullPark1.pdf)<br>About Foster Reservoir (http://www.traveloregon.com/Explore-Oregon/Willamette-Valley/Outdoor-Recreation/Water-Sports/Lakes-and-Reservoirs/Foster-Reservoir.aspx)<br><br>Trout Stocking Schedule - https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=FOSTER+RES&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-53</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value>https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6iMBt1ZNx2LyWsyWRYqVJ2RLNW0C4BSi4I0Yg5X4MO1og_U96gqbQDlHUfLaKIkdIHn4BalDLCYl6leSpuZ5DJ5EG9aoOTAeOnL2dKSojP5X0uJImXwDhOf_bs7K0ZEqQZig3UVWGFp8zU8JLFKv_31rwJP98ZEldaqP2WiAiR</value>
