          <coordinates>
            -124.130359,43.870673,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Green Peter Reservoir - Thistle Cr. Boat Ramp</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v5pH-EduN4tUuuV9wexNUc3-vmqGju7E1MwSHJ5OSbvo_BBtV-JzZlsUcXZRKszRELhMFmSxCkxedra1uBeASeWOcvI_hYohUo18q7HC5V-6_0qzT8NPvxJ6n9csxqsAa83uzc0ZASTkyC0QfL5f08F1YIbkPrq1Q" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Boat ramp on Green Peter Reservoir operated by Linn County Parks & Recreation Department. Amenities include paved ramp and seasonal restrooms.<br> <br>Fish species: rainbow trout, kokanee, bass <br><br>More information (http://www.co.linn.or.us/parks/parks/thistlecreek.html)<br> <br>About Green Peter Reservoir (http://www.nwp.usace.army.mil/include/brochures/GreenPeter_Foster.pdf)<br> <br>Trout Stocking Schedule -https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=GREEN+PETER+RES&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31 ]]></description>
