      <Placemark>
        <name>Green Peter Reservoir - Whitcomb Cr. Park</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v4eRz6MLUeJ-Ug95-vKV1GjFLCXv3Vbh-WH5YDSc5pEFteeRBnoHEeyfZVZLeJ4V1B1BqBPlbmwB6wSeD9sRjs0TqY43I9GUGu3rfj4Bb8ejojVk9IbwrAnP430pyk_3fYYpAIipEPde6MIrb5DnuFncml71ZCVRpsKGQ" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Whitcomb Creek County Park is located on Green Peter Reservoir east of Sweet Home, Oregon. This 328-acre park is managed by the Linn County Parks & Recreation Department. Amenities include basic and group camp sites, boat ramp, group picnic area, bathrooms.<br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout, kokanee, bass<br> <br>About Green Peter Reservoir (http://www.nwp.usace.army.mil/include/brochures/GreenPeter_Foster.pdf)<br> <br>Trout Stocking Schedule - https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=GREEN+PETER+RES&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31]]></description>
