      <Placemark>
        <name>Harriet Lake</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6_qIG6_jheChe90szcEmglIpf4nAmI6w2j7ob-07ROsRRo7OGeOAQyilWARDvq-dEkyVHiCIBK9oZE1WyUOOCRg9otgPeVY_Cs-mTl1zO8i1YuUHBwg2mbg0njRqFCWvSCxNpAJIyql9Z6jEHa3jjf" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>This is a 23-acre reservoir on the Oak Grove Fork of the Clackamas River in the Mount Hood National Forest (http://www.fs.usda.gov/mthood/). Boat ramp is just past campground.<br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout<br> <br>Harriet Lake Campground (http://www.recreation.gov/camping/Lake_Harriet_Or/r/campgroundDetails.do?contractCode=NRSO&parkId=71641&topTabIndex=CampingSpot)<br> <br>Trout Stocking Schedule - https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=HARRIET+LK&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-53</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value>https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6_qIG6_jheChe90szcEmglIpf4nAmI6w2j7ob-07ROsRRo7OGeOAQyilWARDvq-dEkyVHiCIBK9oZE1WyUOOCRg9otgPeVY_Cs-mTl1zO8i1YuUHBwg2mbg0njRqFCWvSCxNpAJIyql9Z6jEHa3jjf</value>
