        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Junction City Pond</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v7KQV2GFS3MCxKPJ7pSPrArGmV0VK0OzxSeF_-XDlbxiTV4jjL75XstQl1GuWRYqDIgEPwWWnCHjurrUjSVJTye3lspR75T14tnPVMyBCrg1ewD9PIHR17yVj5qC2KvXlJima4G3oqCTkrk3Gi5PX-GJpdeS3wO-g" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>This is an 8-acre pond located three miles south of Junction City on the west side of Hwy 99. ODFW stocks the pond regularly with legal and larger rainbow trout making the pond a popular place among anglers.<br> <br>Fish species: rainbow trout<br> <br>Trout Stocking Schedule -https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=JUNCTION+CITY+PD&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31 ]]></description>
