          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Lake Lytle</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v7QpcU7JPQo47-uOgbLpfPHo8Fwr-pSY1xCw3GQrqbjDfs1hGhEj_iNeBGCGkw93xrGUt86GcccwukUWPLY6NWdyq4NGbsNHLrbr7rHg27czsblWjvAuoqkeVnirYbwvN8TuTjcODQ5vVZfHih12yE" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>This is a 65-acre lake located 1/2 mile north of Rockaway Beach on Hwy. 101 The lake sits directly along the east edge of Hwy. 101 at milepost 50. There is a boat ramp off of 12th Street on the north end of the lake. <br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout, largemouth bass, yellow perch, surplus hatchery steelhead when available<br><br>Trout Stocking Schedule -https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=LYTLE+LK&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31 ]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-53</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value>https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v7QpcU7JPQo47-uOgbLpfPHo8Fwr-pSY1xCw3GQrqbjDfs1hGhEj_iNeBGCGkw93xrGUt86GcccwukUWPLY6NWdyq4NGbsNHLrbr7rHg27czsblWjvAuoqkeVnirYbwvN8TuTjcODQ5vVZfHih12yE</value>
          </Data>
