            -123.578167,45.826198,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Lost Lake - Douglas County</name>
        <description><![CDATA[This is a 6-acre lake east of Hwy 101 mid-way between Tahkenitch and Siltcoos lakes, just south of Florence, Ore. on the Oregon coast. Crown Zellerback Campground is situated next to this lake. <br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout<br><br>Trout Stocking Schedule - https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=LOST+LK&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31]]></description>
