      <Placemark>
        <name>McKenzie River - lower</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v7GUTJCjGpzpJihFB8tzh3D3YX4A_2LEMuD7Yfp2NxeMYY9Mx_Spl-_KkhYobWE2-rQ6VeWak9dD8HkAVYKvKkYBFCokQlezAZOHUmInCS8Yl_IQep868JYYKAu-SWuPXm8S-gXXyz9d60vl8G0cnY_Vg8XX1G3m5k" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Rainbow trout from the Oregon Dept. of Fish and Wildlife's Leaburg Fish hatchery are scatter planted by boat throughout this section of the McKenzie River.<br> <br>Fish species: rainbow trout<br> <br>ODFW Recreation Report & regulation updates (http://myodfw.com/recreation-report/fishing-report/willamette-zone/)<br>Trout Stocking Schedule (http://www.dfw.state.or.us/resources/fishing/trout_stocking_schedules/)<br>Fishing Regulations (http://www.eregulations.com/oregon/fishing/)]]></description>
