      <Placemark>
        <name>McKenzie River - upper</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6qqjx4St8cEqZB2XawW-QYzZ6t2q3FnaKE9S-KThEpFWmzvxhgh84ULdwNzb93F9JPbZ0N9bWMTtvGJOZ62wlwuTHwwN-QguA9yVWp7QmqpVlQtnEYaEScV-YpcKsNCjS_cHzgDwDR9Aw5Cpf10DJswYSd2M-JK7A0" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Rainbow trout from the Oregon Dept. of Fish and Wildlife's Leaburg Fish Hatchery are scatter-planted by boat throughout this section of the river.<br> <br>Fish species: rainbow trout<br> <br>Trout Stocking Schedule -https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=MCKENZIE+R-2+%28above+Leaburg+Dam%29&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=]]></description>
