      <Placemark>
        <name>Nedonna Pond</name>
        <description><![CDATA[This is a small pond located just north of Rockaway on Oregon's north coast. The pond is a short distance off Hwy 101 in the Manhattan Beach area, on the right just after crossing the railroad tracks. <br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout <br><br>ODFW Recreation Report & regulation updates (http://myodfw.com/recreation-report/fishing-report/northwest-zone)<br>Trout Stocking Schedule - https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=NEDONNA+PD&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31]]></description>
