      <Placemark>
        <name>North Fork Reservoir Site #2</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6JgE-w4v6o8qWtU0CRouIbCrf5lsGa7SqrKimz9K4wU9OGglDzmJNHqlCsJXV3n13ZBSVMVPCanpdbfk1i7xuHOFRu-EXHMaEX-5gSrFChfZnsIhtWr3k0tQexFu-HBrJlBiz8VrbiYNO_3zGW-acvJg" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>This site is located at the confluence of the North Fork Clackamas River and North Fork Reservoir. It is a small turnout and dirt parking lot north of Hwy 224.<br> <br>Fish species: rainbow trout<br>Trout Stocking Schedule -https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=NORTH+FORK+RES&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31 ]]></description>
