      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>North Georgia Lake</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6l9CHyaEpV_RdUVw65Ag3w8v5wpZ0waDJ3QJPnQmY9aTyTKkPbpEeg9hcz-u7jz2X383pIxmdJJF9zMynMmKH29OsGlhOjqMQ6qnImtM7isxTFnoYzWczs-Wm8hIZlyb-k0rG-0QNDCs6USO0iJSAiNQ" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>The two Georgia Lakes are each about 2 acres in size. There are no signs along the highway marking the lakes and parking is available at several small highway turnouts. The lakes are stocked several times each spring with rainbow trout. The shoreline is forested but brushy. The elevation of the lake is near sea level.<br> <br>Note: Google Maps shows this as Georgia Lake; in fact, this is North Georgia Lake.<br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout<br> <br>Campgrounds: Waxmyrtle (http://www.fs.usda.gov/wps/portal/fsinternet/!ut/p/c4/04_SB8K8xLLM9MSSzPy8xBz9CP0os3gDfxMDT8MwRydLA1cj72BTJw8jAwjQL8h2VAQAzHJMsQ!!/?ss=110612&ttype=recarea&recid=42563&actid=50&navtype=BROWSEBYSUBJECT&position=BROWSEBYSUBJECT&navid=110000000000000&pnavid=&cid=null&pname=Oregon+Dunes+National+Recreation+Area+-+Waxmyrtle+Campground), Lagoon (http://www.fs.usda.gov/wps/portal/fsinternet/!ut/p/c4/04_SB8K8xLLM9MSSzPy8xBz9CP0os3gDfxMDT8MwRydLA1cj72BTJw8jAwjQL8h2VAQAzHJMsQ!!/?ss=110612&ttype=recarea&recid=42557&actid=31&navtype=BROWSEBYSUBJECT&position=BROWSEBYSUBJECT&navid=110000000000000&pnavid=&cid=null&pname=Oregon+Dunes+National+Recreation+Area+-+Lagoon+Campground), Oregon Dunes National Recreation Area (http://www.fs.usda.gov/wps/portal/fsinternet/!ut/p/c5/04_SB8K8xLLM9MSSzPy8xBz9CP0os3gDfxMDT8MwRydLA1cj72DTgBAjAwgAykeaxcN4jhYG_h4eYX5hPgYwefy6w0H24dcPNgEHcDTQ9_PIz03VL8iNMMgycVQEAObEnGA!/dl3/d3/L2dJQSEvUUt3QS9ZQnZ3LzZfME80MEkxVkFCOTBFMktTNUJIMjAwMDAwMDA!/?navtype=BROWSEBYSUBJECT&recid=42465&actid=&navid=110000000000000&pnavid=&ss=110612&position=&ttype=recarea&pname=Siuslaw%20National%20Forest%20-%20Oregon%20Dunes%20National%20Recreation%20Area), Honeyman State Park (http://www.oregonstateparks.org/park_134.php) <br> <br><br>ODFW Recreation Report & regulation updates (http://myodfw.com/recreation-report/fishing-report/northwest-zone)<br>Trout Stocking Schedule https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=GEORGIA+LK%2C+N&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31- ]]></description>
