      <Placemark>
        <name>North Lake</name>
        <description><![CDATA[North Lake is a half-acre lake located within the Siuslaw National Forest (http://www.fs.usda.gov/siuslaw) that lies on the ridgeline above Hebo Lake. Nearby South Lake has a U.S. Forest Service campground that is open year around. The last several miles of road to the lake are unimproved forest road and rough; use caution. It is not advisable to take trailers to this lake. <br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout <br><br>Trout Stocking Schedule - https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=NORTH+LK&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31]]></description>
