          <coordinates>
            -122.935553,45.887678,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Scout Lake</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v4sh8k6eqpFhdfzcwYq_b079M_flUeRDYqzoNcjTks8ZJO4QFyS56kj4YEuqIEDpEsUpv6xLPrgSY0yK1tPcKQqbIcSNsm26ya9YzrixYsR_xdn0EYxBHjZBdClT2NTJPtVd7-3gFgiAMAFa5G1eWU" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>This is a small lake managed by the city of Clatskanie. It is not scheduled for regular trout stocking but sometimes receives hatchery trout by special request. The last mile to this pond is via a forest road accessed by vehicle through a locked gate. Anglers can hike in from the gate or for vehicle access by checking out a gate key from the City of Clatskanie, located at 95 S. Nehalem. To get a key, it is best to call ahead at 503-728-2622.<br> <br>Fish species: rainbow trout<br> <br>ODFW Recreation Report & regulation updates (http://myodfw.com/recreation-report/fishing-report/willamette-zone/)<br>Trout Stocking Schedule (http://www.dfw.state.or.us/resources/fishing/trout_stocking_schedules/)<br>Fishing Regulations (http://www.eregulations.com/oregon/fishing/)]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-53</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value>https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v4sh8k6eqpFhdfzcwYq_b079M_flUeRDYqzoNcjTks8ZJO4QFyS56kj4YEuqIEDpEsUpv6xLPrgSY0yK1tPcKQqbIcSNsm26ya9YzrixYsR_xdn0EYxBHjZBdClT2NTJPtVd7-3gFgiAMAFa5G1eWU</value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
