          <coordinates>
            -123.179655,46.044821,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Sheridan Pond</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v4yeYpoGTktzjc01e0ZCGrvmn_uBvjLgnOPXTV0QN7BwdakHeq8jTVGAAkGI7GTfOUsnFtPwzs8G7xh2MR85cz3F0gts-Xyev5WDcdgc8TLSBtC3xBLUbTxSky1VorZPlLHMeG8YNMToqN2b9j6OV9dpUs" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Sheridan Pond is a 2 1/2-acre pond located on the edge of town. It provides excellent access for families and kids. Good parking. There is an outhouse provided.<br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout<br> <br>Trout Stocking Schedule - https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=SHERIDAN+PD&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-53</styleUrl>
