      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[Shorty's Pond]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[This is a 4-acre pond located within Ivor Davies Nature Park in the city of Molalla. It can be accessed by the fifth St. Trailhead across from Heckard Football Stadium.<br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout<br><br>Trout Stocking Schedule -https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=SHORTY%27S+PD&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31 ]]></description>
