      <Placemark>
        <name>Silver Creek Reservoir</name>
        <description><![CDATA[A 65-acre reservoir on Silver Creek 2.5 miles south of Silverton on Hwy. 214. <br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout, catfish <br>Trout Stocking Schedule - https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=SILVER+CR+RES&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31]]></description>
