            -123.534908,45.048664,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Spring Lake</name>
        <description><![CDATA[A 13-acre lake located on the east side of Hwy. 101 appr. 4 miles north of Garibaldi, Ore. Public access is limited to the highway shoulder. There is no public ramp. Fish stocking is done at the north end of the lake. <br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout, surplus hatchery steelhead when available<br><br>ODFW Recreation Report & regulation updates (http://myodfw.com/recreation-report/fishing-report/northwest-zone)<br>Trout Stocking Schedule - https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=SPRING+LK&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-53</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            -123.945265,45.595633,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>St. Louis Ponds</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6Va72YZXetc5316IpOBWdqBvaWucIIlm3SEfVi5yyO3twzErb5reVnJg4EtmVFHiP14ComOiY0Y2qOXMPPMgkxy1c8Sq5yM_2v2tQBqGB7all-_BpkX8Ly-z1WQ8KEMB3Ise_N66tH9i8ubW0Y779CxEqD" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>This is a 240-acre fishing complex of seven ponds owned and managed jointly by the Oregon Department of Fish and Wildlife and Marion County Parks Department. <br><br>Site has a 2,300-foot paved ADA footpath with turnouts, fishing platforms, restrooms and picnic tables. More primitive trails are also available.<br><br>A gate providing access to the last mile of dirt road to the complex is closed Oct. 1 - March 1, although anglers are still permitted to walk in to fish.<br> <br>Fish species: rainbow trout, white crappie, black crappie, largemouth bass, redear sunfish, green sunfish, bluegill, perch, brown bullhead, channel catfish<br><br>Trout Stocking Schedule - https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=ST+LOUIS+PD&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31]]></description>
