      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Sunset Lake</name>
        <description><![CDATA[A 107-acre lake located appr. 4 miles north of Gearhart, Ore., and west of Hwy. 101.Turn west off of the highway.<br><br>Sunset Lake Park <br>Next to this lake is a 3-acre park with 500 feet of frontage on the lake. <br><br>Facilities include gravel boat ramp, gravel parking area, picnic tables, volleyball and basketball court, bank fishing area and fishing dock. <br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout, largemouth bass, surplus hatchery steelhead when available<br><br>ODFW Recreation Report<br> (https://myodfw.com/recreation-report/fishing-report/northwest-zone)<br>Trout Stocking Schedule -https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=SUNSET+LK.+-+N.+COAST+RANGE&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31 ]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-53</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            -123.929585,46.100975,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Sutton Lake</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v4xwy39nMuT4eYzM_3l6lNgA-dbwU_k-oRpaBREU7pHhruE5aeSZoFUU03arSg-DHot-C9HPbtAS8eN5Y04M8zP8plevIF4_GYRN1IETSrK2JADXCkPOd73YZGcbawnvq0Yax4FG_lbdVE9stbG5FZq" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Sutton Lake is 107 acres in size and appears as two lakes connected by a short channel. Most of the shoreline is private ownership, except for the western shore, which is bounded by Hwy. 101 and a Forest Service day-use area with boat ramp.<br> <br>Fish species: rainbow trout, yellow perch, largemouth bass, cutthroat trout<br> <br>Sutton Campground (http://www.traveloregon.com/Explore-Oregon/Oregon-Coast/Outdoor-Recreation/Fishing/Fishing/Sutton-Campground.aspx)<br> <br>ODFW Recreation Report & regulation updates (http://myodfw.com/recreation-report/fishing-report/willamette-zone/)<br>Trout Stocking Schedule -https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=All&field_waterbody_name_value_1=SUTTON+LK&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31 ]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-53</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value>https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v4xwy39nMuT4eYzM_3l6lNgA-dbwU_k-oRpaBREU7pHhruE5aeSZoFUU03arSg-DHot-C9HPbtAS8eN5Y04M8zP8plevIF4_GYRN1IETSrK2JADXCkPOd73YZGcbawnvq0Yax4FG_lbdVE9stbG5FZq</value>
