      <Placemark>
        <name>Cottage Grove Ponds</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Row River Nature Park Ponds, also known as Cottage Grove Ponds, is a 15-acre site with six ponds. Stocking schedule -- https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule?field_zone_value=6&field_waterbody_name_value_1=ROW+R+NATURE+PK-FMR+COT.GRV+PD&field_planned_stocking_date_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-01-01&field_planned_stocking_date_end_value%5Bdate%5D=2019-12-31]]></description>
